## Navigating Pages

There are **10 pages** total, cycling in order:

| # | Page |
|---|------|
| 1 | INFO |
| 2 | ABILITIES |
| 3 | SKILLS |
| 4 | COMBAT |
| 5 | SPELLCASTING |
| 6 | SPELL SLOTS |
| 7 | FEATURES |
| 8 | CONDITIONS |
| 9 | INVENTORY |
| 10 | CURRENCY |

### Buttons
All buttons in the side panels are **hold-to-repeat** — press and hold to fire repeatedly. Useful for rapidly adjusting values or scrolling through long lists.

| Button | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `PG UP` / `PG DN` | Go to previous / next page |
| `▲ UP` / `▼ DN` | Scroll (on SKILLS page) or navigate fields (in edit mode) |
| `HOME` | Return to INFO page, exit edit mode |

