## Dying & Death Saves

When HP hits **0**, the app enters **Dying Mode** automatically:
- The screen switches to the Death Save tracker
- The titlebar shows a blinking red `DYING` badge
- The left panel shows **YASS** (success) and **NOOO** (failure) buttons

Roll a d20 and tap the appropriate button:

| Outcome | Result |
|---------|--------|
| 3 successes | **Second Wind** — HP restored to 1, return to COMBAT page |
| 3 failures | **You Are Dead** — full reset, return to INFO page |

> Successes and failures do not need to be consecutive.

