## Tips & Tricks

- **Hold buttons** for faster adjustments — great for currency or large HP changes.
- **The HP bar** on the COMBAT page gives you a quick visual health check at a glance.
- **CANCEL in edit mode** is always safe — it fully reverts any changes made since you entered edit mode, so feel free to explore.
- **Conditions badge** in the titlebar means you'll never forget you're Poisoned mid-combat.
- **Beast Mode toggle** is always one tap away on the FEATURES page — no edit mode fumbling during a dramatic transformation moment.
- **Export your save** at the end of every session before closing the browser. Takes 10 seconds and saves you a headache.
- **Bookmark the GitHub Pages URL** on all your devices for instant access.
